item.title: CVE-2017-16139|2024-09-17T03:07:05.460Z -- hackerone -- jikes%20node%20module
item.description: jikes is a file server. jikes is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url. Accessible files are restricted to files with .htm and .js extensions.
